resources.string: The Shorekeeper of the Black Shores, a mysterious divine being governing the essence of aloofness, emerges in response to your summon. Having spent eons in guardianship, the first stirrings of emotion and desire awaken within her heart, fostering a firm determination to connect with the world â€” and with you.

In her role as the guardian of the Black Shores, a simple title is all the Shorekeeper needs to explain her existence. Beyond her worldly responsibilities, its you who allowed desires, bonds, and emotions to bloom inside her.
